The purpose of this study is to determine whether combined therapy with simvastatin and hypotensive drugs (ACEI or ARB) may decrease the blood pressure.

 Moreover, we would like to assess the influence of isolated hypertension on endothelial injury, and on the development of atherosclerosis.

